text:
Dani and Tim are the best! Even if they haven't been my first surfers, I would remember them permanently. We had a lot of fun, great conversations, played games and they cooked delicious food out of the simplest ingredients. They showed me the TV-series "The Expanse" and we ended up binge-watching the whole first season together! :D

@all the cousurfers out there: If they ask you to stay at your place, take the chance, you won't regret it!

@Dani & Tim: Thanks again for those wonderful days, I enjoyed your stay very much! Hope to see you again one day! ;)

