{'id': '16005703', 'text': 'THE BEST HOST I EVER HAD!!!!!!!!!!!!

Ulrika upgraded our trip so much. She took such a good care of us, she lives in an amazing farm, took us to see around, we both wished that we could have stay some more time and agreed that surfing in her place was the pick of our adventure in Sweden

Hoping to hang out again', 'createdDate': '2014-08-10T15:34:14Z', 'experience': 'positive', 'relationshipType': 'surf', 'isPostTrip': False, 'to': {'id': '1006634477'}, 'from': {'id': '2899869', 'publicName': 'Matt Bar', 'publicAddress': {'id': '5604991', 'description': 'Aarhus, Aarhus Municipality, Denmark'}, 'avatarUrl': 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/ht-images.couchsurfing.com/u/2899869/8ac0928a-4aa7-4202-b152-9206a33b8338', 'status': 'yes', 'isVerified': True, 'isDeleted': False, 'blockedBy': None}, 'inverseReference': None, 'response': None}

{'id': '14143457', 'text': "Me and a friend of mine stayed at their apartment for a couple of days, it was so nice, they were very nice to us. We borrowed towels and we could use their washingmachine. They had an extra key aswell, so we could just come and go, that was great! 
They showed us around the city and they were having a party one of the nights, so we just joined, that was good fun :)

I can definetly recommend to ask for a couch at Tommy's place! :)", 'createdDate': '2013-10-31T11:44:31Z', 'experience': 'positive', 'relationshipType': 'surf', 'isPostTrip': False, 'to': {'id': '1000508075'}, 'from': {'id': '1001050785', 'publicName': 'Jonas Mortensen', 'publicAddress': {'id': '9003343', 'description': 'Aarhus, Aarhus Municipality, Denmark'}, 'avatarUrl': 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/ht-images.couchsurfing.com/u/1001050785/cdcbf390-7e7d-4c66-9c30-0bb86c7e2cf4', 'status': 'maybe', 'isVerified': True, 'isDeleted': False, 'blockedBy': None}, 'inverseReference': None, 'response': None}

{'id': '8082862', 'text': "Patricia is a really cute and fun girl. She is full of fun stories and really made me want to visit Brazil - and if all Brazilians are like her, I think I might just stay there ;-)

Absolutely no problem to host, and to my big surprise, she even liked all the weird Danish food I could come up with. We forgot the snaps with the marinated herring though - I'll keep it chilled if you stop by another time!
I really hope to see her again in Denmark, Brazil or perhaps another place on our small planet :-)", 'createdDate': '2011-08-09T13:39:31Z', 'experience': 'positive', 'relationshipType': 'host', 'isPostTrip': False, 'to': {'id': '2160514'}, 'from': {'id': '1921337', 'publicName': 'Peter Bak Petersen', 'publicAddress': {'id': '4626459', 'description': 'Hammel, Favrskov Municipality, Denmark'}, 'avatarUrl': 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/images.couchsurfing.us/CVL0LMK/11525419_l_781bc14538d0b8de333fe3c807e8bdfd.jpg', 'status': 'maybe', 'isVerified': True, 'isDeleted': False, 'blockedBy': None}, 'inverseReference': None, 'response': None}

{'id': '18148496', 'text': "What's to say? Steve is Townsville for me, simple as that. Actually he declined my request, but after a little devious manipulation he let me into his home. 

First of all he's a great guy and a great host - there's nothing else to say. You feel really welcomed, secure and like a part of the household instead of a guest. He don't expect something in return, which obviously makes you want to share something with him even more - I could keep on listing positive values but let's just say he's a prototype of a perfect CS host. 
And a genuinely good guy, and one of the few persons that understands the difference between a discussion and an argument. And he's helpsome. And and and. Steve, I'm gonna see you sooner than later in Townsville (or somewhere else) - stay safe and ZAUCHER the life out of people. ", 'createdDate': '2015-09-05T03:19:36Z', 'experience': 'positive', 'relationshipType': 'other', 'isPostTrip': False, 'to': {'id': '3054317'}, 'from': {'id': '335093', 'publicName': 'Nick Steenberg', 'publicAddress': {'id': '3040241', 'description': 'Aarhus, Central Denmark Region, Denmark'}, 'avatarUrl': 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/images.couchsurfing.us/28QNBS5/8576726_l_74f2f957552429d35ae670ab80a1c58c.jpg', 'status': 'yes', 'isVerified': True, 'isDeleted': False, 'blockedBy': None}, 'inverseReference': None, 'response': None}

{'id': '14254777', 'text': 'Mark is freakingsly awesome. This guy took me in eventhough he knew we would see eachother much due to a conference I had to go to.

This guy helped me with everything - busses, numbers, directions - Mark is the man.

He is very trustful, down to earth and very easy to speak with - next time I hopefully have more time to get to know him.', 'createdDate': '2013-11-19T12:46:31Z', 'experience': 'positive', 'relationshipType': 'surf', 'isPostTrip': False, 'to': {'id': '1001413690'}, 'from': {'id': '335093', 'publicName': 'Nick Steenberg', 'publicAddress': {'id': '3040241', 'description': 'Aarhus, Central Denmark Region, Denmark'}, 'avatarUrl': 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/images.couchsurfing.us/28QNBS5/8576726_l_74f2f957552429d35ae670ab80a1c58c.jpg', 'status': 'yes', 'isVerified': True, 'isDeleted': False, 'blockedBy': None}, 'inverseReference': None, 'response': None}

{'id': '14183980', 'text': "Claudia is great - there's no question about it.

Had the pleasure of hosting her and her friend for a short week and they were very easy to speak to, very easy to satisfy and they were very good at entertaining themselves, since I was away due to exams and other stuff. She is highly trustworthy - that's also the reason why I let her and her friend stay alone in my apartment without a care in the world - I was sure about them.

Great visit - hope to see her again.", 'createdDate': '2013-11-06T20:48:22Z', 'experience': 'positive', 'relationshipType': 'host', 'isPostTrip': False, 'to': {'id': '1003528030'}, 'from': {'id': '335093', 'publicName': 'Nick Steenberg', 'publicAddress': {'id': '3040241', 'description': 'Aarhus, Central Denmark Region, Denmark'}, 'avatarUrl': 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/images.couchsurfing.us/28QNBS5/8576726_l_74f2f957552429d35ae670ab80a1c58c.jpg', 'status': 'yes', 'isVerified': True, 'isDeleted': False, 'blockedBy': None}, 'inverseReference': None, 'response': None}

{'id': '13983014', 'text': "Steph is awesome! I love that girl and hold her in high regard.

She is the kind of surfer you wanna make sure has a good time - and she repays with being down to earth, easy to talk to, fun, openminded and just an incredible person.

I can't wait to meet her and her friends again - if they're just half as cool as she is, I'm gonna feel like home!", 'createdDate': '2013-09-30T19:59:54Z', 'experience': 'positive', 'relationshipType': 'host', 'isPostTrip': False, 'to': {'id': '263981'}, 'from': {'id': '335093', 'publicName': 'Nick Steenberg', 'publicAddress': {'id': '3040241', 'description': 'Aarhus, Central Denmark Region, Denmark'}, 'avatarUrl': 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/images.couchsurfing.us/28QNBS5/8576726_l_74f2f957552429d35ae670ab80a1c58c.jpg', 'status': 'yes', 'isVerified': True, 'isDeleted': False, 'blockedBy': None}, 'inverseReference': None, 'response': None}

{'id': '12907145', 'text': "Overall Experience - Positive?

This can't even be close enough. This girl (and also her fellow-traveler) was the most fantastic persons ever. She's a amazingly person, very deep and yet very easy to be around. A lovely personality and a even more fantastic heart, which are probably as big as a giraffe ;)

