{'id': '1583599', 'text': 'I and My Friend, arrived at 11 p.m. at Antjes place. Antje was so helpful right from the start, she offered to put our bicycles in her basement. Afterwards we went upstairs into her appartment. Antje and her Friend prepared a nice meal, which was just what we, cyclists needed. In every way possible they made us feel like at home; they even let me bake bread and RObert cook dinner in their kitchen - brave people! We talked alot very openly, there place has a wonderful atmosphere, and the view is not bad. Antje and her friend gave us a lot of usefull travel info; thanks alot.  They are experts on the topic Budapest. SO Antje and Ludwig if you ever come to Denmark, then let me know. And if you need contact to some intitutions in relation to your education or work then write me an email. See you in India

Simon and Robert

My finest recommendations and greetings to Antje', 'createdDate': '2008-08-12T14:01:05Z', 'experience': 'positive', 'relationshipType': 'surf', 'isPostTrip': False, 'to': {'id': '637985'}, 'from': {'id': '611918', 'publicName': 'Simon Lykke Justesen', 'publicAddress': {'id': '3317041', 'description': 'Beder, Aarhus Municipality, Denmark'}, 'avatarUrl': 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/images.couchsurfing.us/43SYJUA/12840003_l_4b09858757ed4ca3896a5295875ef63a.jpg', 'status': 'yes', 'isVerified': True, 'isDeleted': False, 'blockedBy': None}, 'inverseReference': None, 'response': None}

{'id': '7057907', 'text': 'My best friend Daniel and I stayed with Kiki for three nights in his nice place.
 
It was the first time we ever tried couchsurfing and we were a bit nervous. That we are not anymore. Kiki was a such a great host. He had so much trust in us, was very welcoming and really a nice person. 

Thanks for giving us such a good start with couchsurfing plus for showing us the program "Going Tribal" :) ', 'createdDate': '2011-04-03T21:26:27Z', 'experience': 'positive', 'relationshipType': 'surf', 'isPostTrip': False, 'to': {'id': '238713'}, 'from': {'id': '2722574', 'publicName': 'Anne Hansen', 'publicAddress': {'id': '5427696', 'description': 'Aarhus, Central Denmark Region, Denmark'}, 'avatarUrl': 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/ht-images.couchsurfing.com/u/2722574/eb5bf972-9eb5-4014-8731-8a512b11fb15', 'status': 'maybe', 'isVerified': True, 'isDeleted': False, 'blockedBy': None}, 'inverseReference': None, 'response': None}
